{"id":2445,"date":"2023-08-24T15:42:51","date_gmt":"2023-08-24T08:42:51","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/tuyensinh.thanhdo.edu.vn\/?p=2445"},"modified":"2023-08-28T10:11:57","modified_gmt":"2023-08-28T03:11:57","slug":"thi-chung-chi-nghiep-vu-huong-dan-du-lich-o-dau","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/tuyensinh.thanhdo.edu.vn\/thi-chung-chi-nghiep-vu-huong-dan-du-lich-o-dau\/","title":{"rendered":"THI CH\u1ee8NG CH\u1ec8 NGHI\u1ec6P V\u1ee4 H\u01af\u1edaNG D\u1eaaN DU L\u1ecaCH \u1ede \u0110\u00c2U?"},"content":{"rendered":"<p><span style=\"font-family: Roboto;\"><em><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 12pt;\">Ch\u1ee9ng ch\u1ec9 nghi\u1ec7p v\u1ee5 h\u01b0\u1edbng d\u1eabn du l\u1ecbch \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o v\u00e0 c\u1ea5p theo quy \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a T\u1ed5ng c\u1ee5c du l\u1ecbch, c\u00f3 gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb xin c\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ed5i th\u1ebb h\u01b0\u1edbng d\u1eabn vi\u00ean du l\u1ecbch n\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ecba\/ qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf tr\u00ean to\u00e0n qu\u1ed1c. Ch\u1ee9ng ch\u1ec9 nghi\u1ec7p v\u1ee5 h\u01b0\u1edbng d\u1eabn du l\u1ecbch c\u00f3 gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb 02 n\u0103m k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb ng\u00e0y c\u1ea5p.<\/span><\/em><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\">Tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u0110\u1ea1i h\u1ecdc Th\u00e0nh \u0110\u00f4 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c T\u1ed5ng c\u1ee5c Du l\u1ecbch cho ph\u00e9p t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c thi, c\u1ea5p Ch\u1ee9ng ch\u1ec9 nghi\u1ec7p v\u1ee5 h\u01b0\u1edbng d\u1eabn du l\u1ecbch n\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ecba, qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf theo gi\u1ea5y ph\u00e9p s\u1ed1 373\/TCDL-LH. Sinh vi\u00ean ng\u00e0nh Vi\u1ec7t Nam h\u1ecdc, Qu\u1ea3n tr\u1ecb Kh\u00e1ch s\u1ea1n, Ng\u00f4n ng\u1eef Anh c\u1ee7a Tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u0110\u1ea1i h\u1ecdc Th\u00e0nh \u0110\u00f4 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi, c\u1ea5p ch\u1ee9ng Ch\u1ee9ng ch\u1ec9 nghi\u1ec7p v\u1ee5 h\u01b0\u1edbng d\u1eabn du l\u1ecbch n\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ecba\/ qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf ngay t\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1eddng m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n h\u1ecdc b\u1ed5 sung ki\u1ebfn th\u1ee9c.\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"text-decoration: underline; font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\"><strong>Th\u00f4ng tin c\u1ee5 th\u1ec3 nh\u01b0 sau:<\/strong><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\"><b>\u0110\u1ed1i t\u01b0\u1ee3ng:<\/b><\/span><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\">Sinh vi\u00ean tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u0110\u1ea1i h\u1ecdc Th\u00e0nh \u0110\u00f4 v\u00e0 c\u00e1c tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u0110\u1ea1i h\u1ecdc Cao \u0111\u1eb3ng kh\u00e1c \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ed1t nghi\u1ec7p.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\">H\u01b0\u1edbng d\u1eabn vi\u00ean du l\u1ecbch c\u00f3 nhu c\u1ea7u \u0111\u1ed5i th\u1ebb h\u01b0\u1edbng d\u1eabn du l\u1ecbch m\u1edbi.<\/span><\/li>\n<li aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\">C\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i t\u01b0\u1ee3ng kh\u00e1c c\u00f3 nhu c\u1ea7u<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\"><b>H\u00ecnh th\u1ee9c thi <\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">g\u1ed3m hai ph\u1ea7n L\u00fd thuy\u1ebft v\u00e0 Th\u1ef1c h\u00e0nh v\u1edbi t\u1ed5ng th\u1eddi l\u01b0\u1ee3ng l\u00e0 170 ph\u00fat.<\/span><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\"><b>Th\u1eddi gian:<\/b><\/span><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Th\u1eddi gian \u00f4n t\u1eadp: <strong>ng\u00e0y 25 v\u00e0 26\/09\/2023<\/strong><\/span><\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Th\u1eddi gian thi d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn: <strong>27\/09\/2023<\/strong><\/span><\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">H\u1ea1n \u0111\u0103ng k\u00fd: \u0111\u1ebfn h\u1ebft ng\u00e0y<strong> 23\/09\/2023<\/strong><\/span><b>\u00a0&#8211; <\/b><a href=\"https:\/\/forms.gle\/ucEZkr7qHHbTbnwx6\"><b>Form \u0111\u0103ng k\u00fd<\/b><\/a><\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\"><strong>H\u1ed3 s\u01a1 \u0111\u0103ng k\u00fd:<\/strong><\/span><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\">01 b\u1ea3n sao ch\u1ee9ng minh nh\u00e2n d\u00e2n ho\u1eb7c th\u1ebb c\u0103n c\u01b0\u1edbc c\u00f4ng d\u00e2n c\u00f4ng ch\u1ee9ng;<\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\">03 \u1ea3nh 3&#215;4 (ghi r\u00f5 h\u1ecd t\u00ean, ng\u00e0y th\u00e1ng n\u0103m sinh \u1edf m\u1eb7t sau);<\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\">01 \u0111\u01a1n \u0111\u0103ng k\u00fd d\u1ef1 thi (theo m\u1eabu);<\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\">01 b\u1ea3n sao c\u00f4ng ch\u1ee9ng b\u1eb1ng t\u1ed1t nghi\u1ec7p tr\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ed9 t\u1eeb trung c\u1ea5p tr\u1edf l\u00ean.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\">M\u1eabu \u0111\u01a1n \u0111\u0103ng k\u00fd <strong><a href=\"https:\/\/docs.google.com\/document\/d\/1lV_ezqGYiMlov0NT-xreJorxFcLHQzmn\/edit\">T\u1ea3i v\u1ec1 t\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y<\/a><\/strong><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\"><b>L\u1ec7 ph\u00ed \u00f4n thi, thi v\u00e0 c\u1ea5p ch\u1ee9ng ch\u1ec9:<\/b><\/span><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\"><b><i>\u0110\u1ed1i v\u1edbi sinh vi\u00ean ng\u00e0nh Vi\u1ec7t Nam h\u1ecdc, Qu\u1ea3n tr\u1ecb Kh\u00e1ch s\u1ea1n, Ng\u00f4n ng\u1eef Anh c\u1ee7a Tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u0110\u1ea1i h\u1ecdc Th\u00e0nh \u0110\u00f4<\/i><\/b><\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"list-style-type: none;\">\n<ul style=\"list-style-type: circle;\">\n<li st